      "logic_summary": "Filter claims to qualifying E&M/wellness CPT codes. Step 1: Count qualifying visits per PCP provider, assign to plurality winner. Step 2: For unassigned members, expand to all ACO providers. Tiebreaker: most recent qualifying visit date."
